data.description:
Super Cute 2 bedroom, 1 bath single-family home centrally located close to Richland Ave in downtown Aiken...only 3 miles from Aiken Regional, 3 miles from USC Aiken, 8 miles from Augusta Technical College and a 1 minute walk to beautiful Eustis Park Playground! 
Great LOCATION!!  
***ASSUMABLE 2.25% VA LOAN!***   
NO CARPET! Laminate wood in living room & bedrooms. Laminate tile in kitchen, bathroom, and hallway. 
Central heat and air, washer/dryer connections, DETACHED CARPORT and a FENCED BACK YARD. STORAGE SHED IN BACK YARD will remain with the property. Move-In Ready ! If room measurements are important please verify. 
Air Conditioner -New Fan -2021 
Kitchen Window, Back Porch construction -2018 
Siding, Gutters -2018 
Washer / Dryer hook ups -2018 
Central Air Installation -2008 
Flooring 2008 
Roof 2007
SOLD AS-IS!  Call for your tour today!
